          <li><strong>Test installs</strong> — WordPress, Webflow, Ghost, headless Astro/Sanity.</li>
          <li><strong>Brief</strong> — 30 SEO articles per tool, mixed transactional + informational intent.</li>
          <li><strong>Measured</strong> — posts live, time-per-post, formatting fidelity, schema validity, internal links inserted.</li>
          <li><strong>Spend</strong> — $1,940 across 10 tools, all on month-to-month pricing.</li>
